quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  53,26,Heewii e malaykaaji e nder kammuuji …ói tefoore majji nafatah huunde tawi wonah caggal de Alla sakkitani wonande mbo O wela O
  53,27,Pellet …ìeen …ìe ngoon…óinaani laakira ho…ìe innira malaykaaji in…óe rew…ìe
  53,28,"Woodanaani …ìe ganndal, alah kove ndewata si wonah sikke, pellet sikke nafatah e goonga hay huunde"
  53,29,…óuurno oon nduntii…óa jikru amen mbo yi…óah si wonah nguurndam aduna
  53,30,"Ko …óoon ganndal mum en haa…ói, pellet ko Alla …ìuri anndude oon majju…óo laawol Makko, ko Kanko kadi …ìuri anndude oon peew…óo"
  53,31,"Ko Alla woodani kala ko woni e kammuuji e leydi ngam o yo…ìa …ìeen bonnu…ìe ko…ìe mbonni ko, O yo…ìa kadi mo∆¥∆¥in…ìe ko mo∆¥∆¥i"
  53,32,"…ìen wo…ó…óitotoo…ìe bakkatuuji maw…ói …óin e pankare […ìe faggitotaako] si wanaa tokoosi …óin. Pellet, Joomi maa ko yaaju…óo yaafuyee. Ko Kanko …ìuri anndude on gila O fu…ó…óunoo on ummaade e leydi, e nde wonuno…óon fu∆¥∆¥annde ka deedi neeniraa…ìe mon. Wata on mantu ko'e mon; ko Kanko …ìuri anndude gom…óu…ìe …ìen"